Titolo: Samurai Warriors 4

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Samurai Warriors 4, known in Japan as Sengoku Musou 4 (戦国無双4), is a hack and slash game by Koei Tecmo, and sequel to Samurai Warriors 3. Unlike past Samurai Warriors games, this one only has Japanese voice overs.
A reboot of the series titled, Samurai Warriors 5, was announced at a Nintendo Direct on February 17, 2021.

Genere: Hack and slash

Valutazione: 74
